  Locus:
    Page: 353
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Patience
---
Patience strengthens the spirit, sweetens the temper, stifles anger,
extinguishes envy, subdues pride, bridles the tongue, restrains the hand,
and tramples upon temptation.
